{"tid":2302832,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"( 社評 ) 任何明顯 挑釁/挑撥/分化/無聊 topic 既 post 唔使覆, 唔使理，由佢沉, 正負評都唔須要。","createTime":"2020-11-27T12:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T15:47:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8b49561c360b2d26fae78726363e1e741e1a91","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T12:10:36.000Z","msg":"( 社評 ) 任何明顯 挑釁/挑撥/分化/無聊 topic 既 post 唔使覆, 唔使理，由佢沉, 正負評都唔須要。<br />\n<br />\n無謂變相幫助推呢類 post 洗版。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">真係忍唔到要覆既, 就用不推文回覆</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">無謂畀個標題浮面。</span><br />\n<br />\n----------------<br />\n<br />\n收到！ 標題同內文都會review<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n--------------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">其實最好都係唔好覆， 由佢沉。</span><br />\n<br />\n因為就算你用 不推文回覆 覆咗個 post,<br />\n佢就有機會用 推文回覆 咋啼駁你，<br />\n咁個 post 又有機會浮返面。"},{"pid":"c0d0f720262a792453ce39175d5e7b8c0e379077","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"（社評）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2302829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2302829</a>"},{"pid":"95008ccc94eada876ab9c9e3d99baf24efeeeb1e","tid":2302832,"uid":308915,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先識善用不推文回覆嚟屌三毛/ATTENTION WHORE?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2303702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2303702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"197140f7a94639748a0f2548cf6e0e893ec123e2","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95008ccc94eada876ab9c9e3d99baf24efeeeb1e","tid":2302832,"uid":308915,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先識善用不推文回覆嚟屌三毛/ATTENTION WHORE?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2303702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2303702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8d5ea2e9c83081a70b2fe64922611d4fad6468","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95008ccc94eada876ab9c9e3d99baf24efeeeb1e","tid":2302832,"uid":308915,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先識善用不推文回覆嚟屌三毛/ATTENTION WHORE?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2303702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2303702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:33:08.000Z","msg":"Pinned"},{"pid":"1ec2b2802e424cce157a95a342e77c4259c0a2b6","tid":2302832,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c459b5c517b7ba76b877620bb46fe45ac270f7","tid":2302832,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b692f5025386f72340efebce7b49ca04ead425","tid":2302832,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"小心有五毛放負/ 踩港撚！所謂踩港撚九成都係五毛，目的旨在消滅香港人對自己嘅自信、自豪同埋感情，製造互不信任、互相猜疑、自暴自棄嘅氛圍，從而穩定政權。以下現象為其中一個表徵：<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇發現，連登總係有一班人，無論你做啲咩嘢，都可以有位話到你，一日到黑不斷講輸啦輸啦冇人做嘢啦移民啦，你唔做嘢佢地會話香港人係奴隸係抵死係癈柴，你去做佢地會話得雞水咁小力有咩用呀邊夠人鬥呀，不如放棄啦快啲移民走佬啦，當社會上有一大班人去做嘅時候佢地就會笑你係送頭係戇鳩，跟住就會講人地食花生睇戲移民呀你地就繼續做傻仔幫港豬移民走啦之類嘅說話內容。佢地真係同路人？大家試諗下，如果真係手足係會俾建議幫手補鑊，即使有唔同意見亦唔會淨係留言不斷笑香港人送頭嘅撚樣，冷嘲熱諷撚一黎只會對件事無幫助，二黎只會散播失敗風同打擊士氣，令人遺憾嘅有唔少傻仔上咗呢一班人嘅當連自己都講埋一份。呢一班究竟係咩人，自己諗。"},{"pid":"70fe642f045aabe48d4b2ebbd5c00dd5e0d7c72d","tid":2302832,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">發現疑似五毛，字裏行間不斷浮現出踩港思維</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ9zjMwJFoLii4SMUurjVE7AD1dFTvRrGFg24VMU8q7Z2?filename=wbsvNxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbsvNxZ.png&h=8383b832&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZPMskDoGEcsJxZ5TxEuQL1t1GofTmv7HP4q4e7mpmpmy?filename=zhFk9Mk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhFk9Mk.png&h=de9a2e08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfb7cb993bb5f5a33e8db9bfe6c57f08c09a2e8e","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T17:08:10.000Z","msg":"（社評）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2302829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2302829</a>"},{"pid":"52319b56fa55fb3da57a972e1beb3f5201468739","tid":2302832,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1906447b9aa30e8a69d14bc5f40b0c840b0e3b71","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"（社評）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2302829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2302829</a>"},{"pid":"09d88b8f85c8a719fb39c68e0db5e834867ad178","tid":2302832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"（社評）三毛最新分化方法 - 分別扮演最激的勇武 同 最左膠的和理非製做分化<br />\